# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:11
translate spanish jamie0_86844818:

    # "I decide to go see Jamie. I walk up to her door and knock twice."
    "Decido ir a ver a Jamie. Me acerco a su puerta y llamo dos veces."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:15
translate spanish jamie0_6d10994a:

    # "After a minute or so, she answers, wearing cloth shorts and a t-shirt tight enough that I can make out the outlines of her nipples through it."
    "Al cabo de un minuto más o menos, me abre, vestida con unos pantalones cortos de tela y una camiseta tan ajustada que puedo distinguir el contorno de sus pezones a través de ella."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:17
translate spanish jamie0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_004.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_004.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:18
translate spanish jamie0_ae29242d:

    # gnd "Oh hi, [pcname]. What's up?"
    gnd "Hola, [pcname]. ¿Qué tal?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:21
translate spanish jamie0_1142edfa:

    # pc "I was just wondering what you were up to."
    pc "Me preguntaba qué estabas haciendo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:23
translate spanish jamie0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_005.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_005.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:24
translate spanish jamie0_5c68d96a:

    # gnd "I'm just watching TV. Want to come inside and hang out?"
    gnd "Solo estoy viendo la tele. ¿Quieres pasar y quedarte un rato?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:27
translate spanish jamie0_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:30
translate spanish jamie0_8530d6f7:

    # pc "Not right now."
    pc "Ahora mismo no."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:35
translate spanish jamie0_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_009b.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:36
translate spanish jamie0_7761ed77:

    # gnd "I'm sorry, I'm not really feeling up to going anywhere tonight."
    gnd "Lo siento, la verdad es que no me apetece salir esta noche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:37
translate spanish jamie0_e3b9539d:

    # gnd "I'm in the middle of a TV show and already dressed for bed."
    gnd "Estoy viendo una serie y ya me he puesto el pijama."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:39
translate spanish jamie0_9c09b9dd:

    # gnd "Do you want to come inside and chat a bit though?"
    gnd "¿Pero quieres entrar a charlar un rato?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:47
translate spanish jamie0_4f724fa8:

    # gnd "What?"
    gnd "¿Qué?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:48
translate spanish jamie0_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Nos vemos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:49
translate spanish jamie0_2c2201d1:

    # gnd "Uh okay, see you later then."
    gnd "Eh, vale, nos vemos luego entonces."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:51
translate spanish jamie0_74706d57:

    # "She looks disappointed as she shuts the door and I walk back over to my house."
    "Parece decepcionada mientras cierra la puerta y yo vuelvo a mi casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:56
translate spanish leavejamie_fc2cf32e:

    # gnd "Okay, maybe we can do something some other time?"
    gnd "Vale, ¿quizás podamos hacer algo en otra ocasión?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:57
translate spanish leavejamie_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:58
translate spanish leavejamie_60ba3b2f:

    # gnd "Well, I'll see you later then."
    gnd "Bueno, pues hasta luego."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:59
translate spanish leavejamie_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Nos vemos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:60
translate spanish leavejamie_74706d57:

    # "She looks disappointed as she shuts the door and I walk back over to my house."
    "Parece decepcionada mientras cierra la puerta y yo vuelvo a mi casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:68
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_b827e096:

    # "She leads me to the living room, where the TV is paused on a show that I don't recognize."
    "Me lleva al salón, donde la tele está en pausa en un programa que no reconozco."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:69
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_1410557b:

    # gnd "I was just trying to finish up this series that I've been watching before school starts up again."
    gnd "Estaba intentando terminar esta serie que he estado viendo antes de que empiecen las clases de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:70
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_442eef5c:

    # pc "Cool. I barely watch any TV anymore."
    pc "Genial. Ya casi no veo la tele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:71
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_e0203869:

    # gnd "Really? I love TV. I probably watch too much."
    gnd "¿En serio? Me encanta la tele. Probablemente la veo demasiado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:73
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_5407ea16:

    # "We sit there for a few moments in an awkward silence. There are a couple times when Jamie seems like she wants to say something, but doesn't."
    "Nos quedamos allí sentados unos momentos en un silencio incómodo. Hay un par de ocasiones en las que Jamie parece querer decir algo, pero no lo hace."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:74
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_58b01cd5:

    # "It feels very strange, like she is uncomfortable with me for some reason. Like there is something between us."
    "Se siente muy extraño, como si ella se sintiera incómoda conmigo por alguna razón. Como si hubiera algo entre nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:75
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_396a0d53:

    # "I have to break this silence with literally any conversation."
    "Tengo que romper este silencio con cualquier conversación, literalmente."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:76
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_1171aaad:

    # pc "Oh, I have a cell phone now."
    pc "Ah, ahora tengo móvil."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:78
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_5c1dfc7a:

    # gnd "Awesome, what's your number?"
    gnd "Genial, ¿cuál es tu número?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:79
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_53b692f6:

    # "I tell her my new phone number and she puts it into her phone."
    "Le digo mi nuevo número de teléfono y ella lo guarda en el suyo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:81
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_b9feb81a:

    # "Then she turns her phone around and holds it up to take a picture of herself."
    "Luego le da la vuelta al móvil y lo sostiene para hacerse una foto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:83
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_5ad0b0e8:

    # gnd "I sent you a text message, along with a picture of me so you can add me into your contacts, and we can chat whenever."
    gnd "Te he enviado un mensaje de texto, junto con una foto mía para que puedas añadirme a tus contactos, y así podamos charlar cuando quieras."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:88
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_ea0a9e4e:

    # pc "I got it. I'll just add you to my contacts real quick."
    pc "Ya lo tengo. Te voy a añadir a mis contactos en un momento."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:89
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_d7eecc80:

    # pc "And done."
    pc "Y listo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:90
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_7a48c010:

    # gnd "Awesome."
    gnd "Genial."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:93
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_a06bb2fa:

    # pc "Great. I'll be sure to add you as soon as I get back home and get the phone set up."
    pc "Estupendo. Te añadiré en cuanto llegue a casa y configure el teléfono."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:95
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_570f0e90:

    # "She sits on the couch next to me, leaning back against the arm rest to face me, her bare legs folded underneath her."
    "Se sienta en el sofá a mi lado, recostándose contra el reposabrazos para mirarme, con las piernas desnudas cruzadas debajo de ella."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:96
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_06525d7f:

    # gnd "Do you want to watch my TV show with me?"
    gnd "¿Quieres ver mi serie conmigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:97
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:98
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_49f2ae65:

    # gnd "It's called The Nieces of Callahan. Have you ever watched any of it?"
    gnd "Se llama Las sobrinas de Callahan. ¿La has visto alguna vez?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:99
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_c7fa5d68:

    # pc "Nope."
    pc "No."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:100
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_f8a2b09a:

    # gnd "Well I'm sure you'll be completely lost, but I'll try to catch you up."
    gnd "Bueno, seguro que te vas a perder por completo, pero intentaré ponerte al día."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:102
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_fb6f3632:

    # "She plays the show, but talks pretty much the whole time through it, explaining which character was which, who was sleeping with who, and which characters she liked and hated."
    "Pone la serie, pero habla prácticamente todo el tiempo mientras la vemos, explicando qué personaje era cuál, quién se acostaba con quién y qué personajes le gustaban y cuáles odiaba."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:103
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_8a51ccf8:

    # "The show doesn't interest me too much, but as we sit together, she moves closer and closer, until our sides are touching."
    "La serie no me interesa demasiado, pero mientras estamos sentados juntos, ella se va acercando cada vez más, hasta que nuestros costados se tocan."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:104
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_df180490:

    # "I think about putting an arm around her shoulder, but I'm not sure what she would think about it."
    "Pienso en ponerle un brazo sobre el hombro, pero no estoy seguro de qué pensaría ella al respecto."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:105
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_02a91ff8:

    # "Still, being there next to her is nice."
    "Aun así, estar ahí a su lado es agradable."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:106
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_7c085331:

    # "Finally, the show ends."
    "Por fin, termina la serie."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:108
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_616bf526:

    # gnd "Did you like it?"
    gnd "¿Te ha gustado?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:109
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_28b82c1c:

    # pc "Honestly, I couldn't really follow it, but what I saw was okay."
    pc "La verdad es que no he podido seguirlo muy bien, pero lo que he visto estaba bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:110
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_82d9fc6f:

    # gnd "Yeah, you kind of have to watch it from the beginning."
    gnd "Sí, hay que verlo desde el principio."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:111
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_95fb6df8:

    # gnd "Thanks for sitting through it with me anyways. That was nice."
    gnd "Gracias por quedarte a verlo conmigo de todas formas. Ha estado bien."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:112
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_4eb9bd3a:

    # pc "Yeah it was. I enjoyed it."
    pc "Sí, lo ha estado. Me ha gustado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:115
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_0bde0b2d:

    # gnd "I'm so glad you're back in town. I know we didn't hang out much before you left, but I've always liked you and thought about you."
    gnd "Me alegro mucho de que hayas vuelto a la ciudad. Sé que no salíamos mucho antes de que te fueras, pero siempre me has caído bien y he pensado en ti."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:116
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_48b6a79b:

    # pc "Yeah, we had some good times when we were younger."
    pc "Sí, lo pasamos bien cuando éramos más jóvenes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:117
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_234edbbb:

    # gnd "Yeah we did. I wish we would have stayed friends through high school. I made a lot of bad decisions then."
    gnd "Sí, así es. Ojalá hubiéramos seguido siendo amigos durante el instituto. Tomé muchas decisiones equivocadas por aquel entonces."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:118
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_ce0b88b7:

    # pc "I think we all did."
    pc "Creo que todos las tomamos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:119
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_ec3ba06e:

    # gnd "Ain't that the truth."
    gnd "Es la pura verdad."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:121
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_68579f4f:

    # "She smiles at me, and we stand awkwardly for a few moments."
    "Ella me sonríe y nos quedamos allí de pie, un poco incómodos, durante unos instantes."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:122
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_5a0cac5d:

    # pc "Anyways, I better get home."
    pc "Bueno, mejor me voy a casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:124
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_792d2ec7:

    # gnd "Okay, well thanks for coming to see me. Stop by anytime or send me a text if you want to chat."
    gnd "Vale, pues gracias por venir a verme. Pásate cuando quieras o envíame un mensaje si te apetece charlar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:126
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_007.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:127
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_598f8960:

    # gnd "See you later."
    gnd "Hasta luego."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/jamie0.rpy:129
translate spanish tvchatwithjamie_3608be46:

    # "She smiles and waves as I walk out the door, shutting it behind me, and walk over to my house."
    "Ella sonríe y me dice adiós con la mano mientras salgo por la puerta, la cierro detrás de mí y me dirijo a mi casa."

